OL,3,CIsrael renews attacks on Lebanon as
OL,4,CNetanyahu warns 'many surprises' ahead
OL,6,FIsrael attacked Beirut and southern
OL,7,FLebanon again early on Sunday, killing
OL,8,Fmore than 12 people, following a
OL,9,Fstrike on an oil facility in Tehran
OL,10,Fthat shook the Iranian capital.
OL,12,FThe Israeli military said it would
OL,13,F"not allow Iranian terrorist elements
OL,14,Fto establish themselves in Lebanese
OL,15,Fterritory", adding that it was
OL,16,Ftargeting commanders of the Lebanon
OL,17,Fbranch of Iran's Revolutionary Guards'
OL,18,FQuds Force.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/19
