OL,3,CIsrael renews attacks on Lebanon as
OL,4,CNetanyahu warns 'many surprises' ahead
OL,6,F"As bad as things are today, they are
OL,7,Fset to get even worse," she warned.
OL,8,F"The choice is clear: stay on a path
OL,9,Fof death and destruction, or commit to
OL,10,Frestraint, engagement and dialogue."
OL,12,FJust over one week ago, Israel and the
OL,13,FUS launched what they described as
OL,14,F"pre-emptive" strikes against Iran,
OL,15,Fwhich they view as intent on acquiring
OL,16,Fnuclear weapons ` shortly after a
OL,17,Fround of negotiations.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@WO]pD@AOUrD@dO]
