OL,3,CIsrael renews attacks on Lebanon as
OL,4,CNetanyahu warns 'many surprises' ahead
OL,6,FDonald Trump has spent the weekend
OL,7,Fhitting out at Keir Starmer over the
OL,8,FUK's decision not to join initial US-
OL,9,FIsraeli strikes in Iran.
OL,11,FThe UK initially would not let the US
OL,12,Fuse its military bases to facilitate
OL,13,Fstrikes on Iran, but later agreed to
OL,14,Fallow their use for "specific
OL,15,Fdefensive operations", with the US
OL,16,Fsending bomber planes to RAF Fairford
OL,17,Fin Gloucestershire this weekend.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
