OL,3,CIsrael renews attacks on Lebanon as
OL,4,CNetanyahu warns 'many surprises' ahead
OL,6,FPreparations have been made to send
OL,7,Faircraft carrier HMS Prince of Wales
OL,8,Fto the Middle East region, and while
OL,9,Fno decisions have been made, Trump did
OL,10,Fnot appear impressed by the offer.
OL,12,FIn a post on his Truth Social
OL,13,Fplatform, the US president wrote: "The
OL,14,FUnited Kingdom, our once Great Ally,
OL,15,Fmaybe the Greatest of them all, is
OL,16,Ffinally giving serious thought to
OL,17,Fsending two aircraft carriers to the
OL,18,FMiddle East.
OL,26,@uD@cOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/19
