OL,3,CIsrael renews attacks on Lebanon as
OL,4,CNetanyahu warns 'many surprises' ahead
OL,6,F"That's OK, Prime Minister Starmer, we
OL,7,Fdon't need them any longer ` But we
OL,8,Fwill remember. We don't need people
OL,9,Fthat join Wars after we've already
OL,10,Fwon!"
OL,12,FThe latest round of violence in the
OL,13,FMiddle East has killed at least 1,230
OL,14,Fpeople in Iran and 11 in Israel,
OL,15,Faccording to officials, while the
OL,16,Fbodies of six US troops killed in
OL,17,FKuwait were repatriated last night.
