OL,3,CIsrael renews attacks on Lebanon as
OL,4,CNetanyahu warns 'many surprises' ahead
OL,6,FThe latest strikes in Lebanon followed
OL,7,Fan attack on an oil storage facility
OL,8,Fin Tehran on Saturday night, with
OL,9,FIranian state media blaming "the US
OL,10,Fand the Zionist regime".
OL,12,FIt came as Israeli Prime Minister
OL,13,FBenjamin Netanyahu promised "many
OL,14,Fsurprises" for the next phase of the
OL,15,Fconflict, adding: "We have many more
OL,16,Ftargets, and I will not elaborate."
OL,18,FITV News correspondents recap
OL,19,FSaturday's developments as the Middle
OL,20,FEast war entered its second week
OL,26,@qD@]OUrD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/19
