OL,3,CIsrael renews attacks on Lebanon as
OL,4,CNetanyahu warns 'many surprises' ahead
OL,6,FElsewhere in the region, Kuwait
OL,7,Fauthorities said two border guards
OL,8,Fwere killed when the Gulf country was
OL,9,Fhit by a swarm of missiles and drones.
OL,11,FThe Interior Ministry said only that
OL,12,Fthe guards were killed "while
OL,13,Fperforming their national duty." No
OL,14,Fother details were available.
OL,16,FA wave of drone attacks also targeted
OL,17,Fcritical infrastructure in the oil-
OL,18,Frich country, including fuel tanks at
OL,19,FKuwait International Airport and a
OL,20,Fgovernment building in Kuwait City.
OL,26,@tD@XOUuD@`O]
