OL,3,CIsrael renews attacks on Lebanon as
OL,4,CNetanyahu warns 'many surprises' ahead
OL,6,FThree people were wounded in a missile
OL,7,Fattack in Bahrain as shrapnel fell
OL,8,Fover a university building in Muharraq
OL,9,Fcity on Sunday morning, according to
OL,10,Fthe country's Interior Ministry.
OL,12,FBahrain said an Iranian drone attack
OL,13,Fcaused "material damage" to a
OL,14,Fdesalination plant ` the first time an
OL,15,FGulf country said Iran has struck a
OL,16,Fdesalination plant during the nine-day
OL,17,Fwar.
OL,26,@uD@HOUuD@XO]
