OL,3,CIsrael renews attacks on Lebanon as
OL,4,CNetanyahu warns 'many surprises' ahead
OL,6,FHundreds of desalination plants sit
OL,7,Falong the Persian Gulf coast, and the
OL,8,Fregion relies heavily on them for
OL,9,Ftheir water.
OL,11,FEarlier on Sunday, Iran's Foreign
OL,12,FMinister Abbas Araghchi said a US
OL,13,Fairstrike damaged an Iranian
OL,14,Fdesalination plant on Qeshm Island. He
OL,15,Fwarned that in doing so, "the US set
OL,16,Fthis precedent, not Iran".
OL,26,@wD@ZOUxD@YO]
