OL,3,CIsrael renews attacks on Lebanon as
OL,4,CNetanyahu warns 'many surprises' ahead
OL,6,FEarlier on Sunday, the United Arab
OL,7,FEmirates said debris from an aerial
OL,8,Finterception fell onto a vehicle and
OL,9,Fkilled a driver. Four people have now
OL,10,Fbeen killed in the UAE since the war
OL,11,Fbegan. Authorities have said all were
OL,12,Fforeign nationals.
OL,14,FThe UAE urged residents to stay
OL,15,Findoors Sunday morning as its military
OL,16,Fresponded to a drone attack.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/19
