OL,3,CIsrael renews attacks on Lebanon as
OL,4,CNetanyahu warns 'many surprises' ahead
OL,6,FSaudi Arabia said it destroyed a drone
OL,7,Fheaded toward its vast Shaybah oil
OL,8,Ffield on Sunday and shot down four
OL,9,Fdrones over the capital, Riyadh,
OL,10,Fincluding one aimed at the diplomatic
OL,11,Fquarter.
OL,13,FThree Iraqi security officials,
OL,14,Fspeaking anonymously, said a missile
OL,15,Flanded on the helicopter landing pad
OL,16,Fin the US Embassy complex in Baghdad.
OL,18,FAn embassy spokesperson declined to
OL,19,Fcomment. There were no reports of
OL,20,Fcasualties.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/19
