OL,3,CIsrael renews attacks on Lebanon as
OL,4,CNetanyahu warns 'many surprises' ahead
OL,6,FIt was the first reported strike to
OL,7,Fland in Baghdad's heavily fortified
OL,8,FGreen Zone since the Iran war began.
OL,9,FIran and allied Iraqi militias have
OL,10,Flaunched dozens of attacks on US
OL,11,Fmilitary bases and other facilities in
OL,12,FIraq since then.
OL,14,FIraq's caretaker Prime Minister
OL,15,FMohammed Shia al-Sudani called the
OL,16,Fembassy attack a "terrorist act"
OL,17,Fcarried out by "rogue groups".
