OL,3,CIsrael renews attacks on Lebanon as
OL,4,CNetanyahu warns 'many surprises' ahead
OL,6,FThe latest strikes come despite
OL,7,FIranian President Masoud Pezeshkian
OL,8,Fapologising on Saturday for attacks on
OL,9,F"neighbouring countries", suggesting
OL,10,Fit would not target them "unless
OL,11,Fattacked first".
OL,13,FThere appears to be a rift between
OL,14,Fpoliticians looking to de-escalate the
OL,15,Fwar and others committed to battling
OL,16,Fthe United States and Israel, which
OL,17,Fcould complicate any diplomatic
OL,18,Fefforts.
OL,26,@qD@AOU
