OL,3,CIsrael renews attacks on Lebanon as
OL,4,CNetanyahu warns 'many surprises' ahead
OL,6,FHard-line judiciary chief Gholam
OL,7,FHossein Mohseni-Ejei, another member
OL,8,Fof the three-man leadership council,
OL,9,Fsuggested that war strategy will not
OL,10,Fchange.
OL,12,F"The geography of some countries in
OL,13,Fthe region ` both overtly and covertly
OL,14,F` is in the hands of the enemy, and
OL,15,Fthose points are used against our
OL,16,Fcountry in acts of aggression. Intense
OL,17,Fattacks on these targets will
OL,18,Fcontinue," he posted on X.
OL,26,@tD@AOUzD@JO]
