OL,3,CIsrael renews attacks on Lebanon as
OL,4,CNetanyahu warns 'many surprises' ahead
OL,6,FIran's UN mission later suggested,
OL,7,Fwithout offering evidence, that
OL,8,Fstrikes on nonmilitary sites "may have
OL,9,Fresulted from interception by US
OL,10,Felectronic defence systems".
OL,12,FLate on Saturday, top Iranian security
OL,13,Fofficial Ali Larijani asserted in an
OL,14,Faddress carried by state media that
OL,15,F"our leaders are united on this issue
OL,16,Fand have no disagreements with one
OL,17,Fanother".
